[CLS] <s>Hi, How are you doing today?</s>
<s>a bit concerned as I am afraid that my job will let go more staff like they did a couple months ago.</s>
<s>Ah im sorry to hear that. Best advice i can give is to play for exactly that.</s>
<s>I am afraid id they let more people go I may be let go as well.</s>
<s>Like maybe get your resume cleaned up, cast some lines out for employment now, checked linkdin, worst come to worst, make sure you know how to fill out unemployment for the future. If you have a plan already it will ease some of that anxiety that will come from this tough situation.</s>
<s>At my age, i fo not want to look for another job, i prefer to stay at this job until I retire. So that makes me anxious.</s>
<s>Unfortunately, life doesnt always do what we want. What we can do is plan ahead though. It will make you less anxious if you know you have a back up plan.</s>
<s>I hate the thought that i may have to start over.</s>
<s>I know that is a really rough thing to go through. Do you have anyone at home you can talk to as well? Just letting it out helps sometimes.</s>
<s>No, I do not, but I can call a friend.</s>
<s>It might make you feel a bit better, maybe they can give you some perspective as well.</s>

<s>How did you cope up with the situation?</s>
<s>I talked to my friends about it a lot, and tried to keep myself occupied with lots of activities. I also deleted old messages from my partner so I didn' t dwell on the past as much.</s>
<s>How does talking to friends help?</s>
<s>It depends on the situation, but for me I had a lot of unresolved feelings from not getting proper closure, so ranting to my friends about how my partner hurt me helped satisfy that. Do you have friends you feel comfortable talking to about this?</s>

[CLS] <s>I got kicked out of the home I was living in.</s>
<s>Wow I am really sorry. Were you living with family, or with friends?</s>
<s>I lived in a rented room.</s>
<s>So you were thrown out from a place you were renting? Did you do anything wrong?</s>
<s>No. The renter said he just wanted me out. He also charged me ninety extra dollars.</s>
<s>Wow that is illegal. Do you know that there are organisations that can help you with this sort of thing?</s>
<s>No. I did not. I asked my exboyfriend at the time for advice. He just say to pay him and move.</s>
<s>I think that that was bad advice to be honest. I think that you are being ripped off. Do not worry, there are things that you can do about it!</s>
<s>That is reassuring. I would like action to be taken for justice.</s>
<s>You are definitely entitled to it. Do you have somewhere else to live in the meantime?</s>
<s>I have a couch to crash on. Another guy said I could store my furniture in his basement. But no official room.</s>
<s>It' s a precarious position to be in, especially during a pandemic. Do you have any family members who might help?</s>
<s>Yes, I could call my mother. She has a room to stay in. But I only have the money to drive to her home, not the money for a rental truck to move all my stuff.</s>
<s>Would any family members be prepared to loan you money or a vehicle?</s>
<s>I could ask my aunt to use her car, she has an SUV, where as I drive a sedan.</s>
<s>How much stuff do you have that needs to be moved?</s>
<s>Queen bed, bed frame, small desk, roll chair, bookshelf, rug, boxes of kitchen stuff, etc.</s>
<s>Try not to worry too much - I was in this position once myself and it did all turn out for the best though it was very scary at the time.</s>
<s>Yes, I feel almost numb from the depression. Like non of my stuff matters, only that I am physically safe.</s>
<s>I think it would be a good idea for you to try and get medical help for your depression.</s>
<s>Yes, I agree. Asking for help is a plan.</s>
<s>It isn't really about feeling safe, actually!</s>
<s>That's true. I guess that's what my therapist said.</s>========

<s>Yes, I have had back surgery, tried Yoga, and chiropractors, and physical therapy. Nothing has worked.</s>
<s>I know that constant pain is definitely up there with one of the most difficult things a person can deal with. It can also affect your mental health over time but there are solutions out there that can help.</s>
<s>It is just hard, waking up in the middle of the night with pain and not being able to go back to sleep. It drives me nuts some days and I just stay away from everyone.</s>

<s>I try to hide the pain from my family because the man of the house is suppose to be strong and provide for his family. I have a very loving wife and a set of twin boys that just turned 13. I am blessed in so many ways but I still seem to have to suffer to enjoy it.</s>
<s>if I' m being honest I can relate to this. I have a young son and a small family myself. I have had problems with my hearing and tinnitus that is manageable at the moment but constant. in feels like nobody understands just how difficult this can be.</s>
<s>I feel your pain, I have came a long way in managing the pain mentally. I try to block it out and keep my mind busy to not think about it. Sometimes it works, sometimes it doesn' t.</s>

[CLS] <s>Hello there, how is life treating you?</s>
<s>Hello! Life is treating me fair, what about you?</s>
<s>Well, I' ve been a bit worried this year due to Covid and everything. Have you been worrying about anything?</s>
<s>Yes, not covid tho. Mostly, it' s academics. It paralyses me.</s>
<s>Do you work in academia then? Or are you a student?</s>
<s>I am a college student, and I miss my high school days.</s>
<s>So you feel that life was more simple when you were still in high school?</s>
<s>Yes, schoolwork wise. Now, I can never stay on top.</s>
<s>I think that it is quite usual to feel a bit disorientated when transitioning from school to college. It is strange to feel like an adult all of a sudden.</s>
<s>Do you have any experience with that?</s>
<s>Yes I do. It took me quite a long time to adjust to college in my first year too.</s>
<s>Woah, I am sorry it was rough for you.</s>
<s>It was a bit but I think that it was not just me. It' s a huge life change. Is your problem mainly with your grades or are there other issues?.</s>

[CLS] <s>Hello there, how is life treating you?</s>
<s>Hello! Life is treating me fair, what about you?</s>
<s>Well, I' ve been a bit worried this year due to Covid and everything. Have you been worrying about anything?</s>

<s>Yes, schoolwork wise. Now, I can never stay on top.</s>

<s>That is understandable. You said that they are acting like your kids and not responding to your way of communicating? Am i right?</s>

[CLS] <s>Hello how are you? I am here to support you.</s>
<s>Oh, hi! Thank you. I was just talking to myself. lol No one showed up the last few times I tried to do this.</s>
<s>How can I help support you today? I know these are tough times and we all need to be heard.</s>
<s>I' m just looking for someone new to talk to. I don' t really feel like I can express my actual feelings in my current living arrangement.</s>
<s>I understand. I have had to stay by myself for most of the year due to the pandemic. That has been hard.</s>
<s>I' ve heard the pandemic has affected a lot of people. I' m always alone anyway... or with my roommate, so I haven' t noticed much of a difference.. It' s difficult when we have absolutely nothing in common..</s>
<s>Have you tried different games that help you get to know each other? Maybe try a movie or series. I loved Sweet Magnolia' s on Netflix.</s>
<s>I' m mainly worried that she' ll throw me out of the house and I' ll have no where to live. Oh god forbid we watch a movie. She' s too obsessed with CNN to watch anything else. She' s become brainwashed by the tabloid media...</s>
<s>Oh my goodness. The good thing is there is a moratorium on evictions so she would not be able to do that legally. CNN can be overwhelming. Try giving her some type of distraction. Suggest yoga or some type of bonding. I think 24/ 7 news is problematic but here to stay.</s>
<s>I actually do yoga every evening. She hates it. I' m living in her home without a lease, so I wonder if she can just tell me to leave. I can' t imagine why anyone would want to watch the news for more than to just catch up( If you like lies and nonsense)</s>
<s>As long as you have property there she would have to formally evict you. That is the good news..</s>
<s>That is good news. <s>I live on my own... well at least as the only human. I have a dog.</s>
<s>That is great that you at least have your dog. They' re great companion.</s>

[CLS] <s>Hello.</s>
<s>Hi.</s>
<s>What can I help you with today?</s>
<s>I' ve been feeling really sad lately. I think I have depression.</s>
<s>Is there any reason that triggered your sadness?</s>
<s>It' s 2020 so there' s been a lot going on, but I' ve been struggling with this before all of that. 2020 has made it much worse though.</s>
<s>I am sorry you feel this way. Do you live with friends or family?</s>
<s>I live on my own... well at least as the only human. I have a dog.</s>
<s>That is great that you at least have your dog. They' re great companion.</s>
<s>She is amazing and my love and joy. On days I feel I cannot get out of bed and I don' t have work, I get up for her.</s>
<s>How about you hang out once a week with your friends and share your problem with them?</s>

[CLS] <s>Hello there, how are we doing today?</s>
<s>Hi ineed help, parents are putting to much pressure on me.</s>
<s>Im sorry to hear that your parents are putting to much pressure on you, do you want to go into further detail?</s>
<s>Yes. For some reason my parents put so much pressure on me to do well in school its killing me..</s>
<s>I am sure they just want what is best, but i have been there as a teen as well. What matters the most is how you feel. Have you talked to them?</s>
<s>No. i haven' t im scared they will be so mad at me telling them how i feel.</s>
<s>Have you tried talking to a school counselor?</s>
<s>No, i haven' t but i will take your advice and talk to a counselor.</s>
<s>It is a good first step. Also depending how old you are some therapists work on a sliding scale or wave fees if you cant afford it. The counselor may be able to act as a mediator between you and your parents.</s>
<s>That' s great. it will definitely ease some tensions.</s>
<s>I wouldnt hold off to long as these types of problems tend to brew and just get stronger. I know you will feel better once you let it out there. I hope it is even helping now.</s>
<s>I will talk to the counsellor first and see what they say. i feel so much better now.</s>
<s>I am very happy for you.</s>

[CLS] <s>Hello how are you?</s>
<s>Hi. How are you?</s>
<s>Doing good and yourself?</s>
<s>I've been better. Just got into a major argument with my parents.</s>
<s>That can be tough can you tell me what the argument was about?</s>
<s>They don't agree with the girl I have been dating.</s>
<s>So, why do you think they think that?</s>
<s>Because of her race. She is black.</s>
<s>I can see why you would be upset about that. So, that is the only reason they don' t approve. At this point when they are not as upset you may want to share all the reason she a great girlfriend. If it is based totally on race not sure you can change their minds.</s>
<s>You are right. But I'm afraid it is solely based on race. She is such a great person. I wish they could look past her race.</s><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad>========

[CLS] <s>Hey it is getting difficult day by day.</s>

<s>We are unable to meet our friends and families especially during holidays like Thanksgiving and Christmas.</s>

[CLS] <s>how you doing?</s>
<s>hii. could you please help to come out of fear from my friend who became physco.</s>
<s>i can imagine how you are feeling right now, but can you explain better how the situation is?</s>
<s>he is one of the best friends in the group. we are 10 members, when went to party after drunk he took pictures with us when we were half nude. Now he blackmailing by that phots and asking money.</s>
<s>i know you might be feeling betrayed right now, a friend should not have behaved like that.</s>
<s>yes, he should not, another friend family suffered lot. she attempt suicide. so i am scaring a lot.</s>
<s>there should be someone you can try to confined in, i know you did wrong by drinking, but you need to open up to someone, cop your parent or someone you trust.</s>
<s>i thought so, wanted to share with my hubby but scaring that he might think i cheated him but in real we never do anything. it is a group a party. thank you for ur time,</s>
<s>do you think he might be jealous of you by lying to his friend?</s>

<s>Are you raising them alone?</s>

<s>wow, that' s super frustrating! I would be pretty upset too. How did you find out?</s>
<s>I overheard a private phone call with his wife. He said that despite the tough year the company is having, he' s expecting to get a large bonus because he cut costs so drastically. I also heard him discuss it with the director of sales. They were strategizing how to shift the costs around to cover the tracks. I heard the words" good thing we have the power, if others knew we were getting our full bonuses they' d walk out"</s>
<s>wow... did anyone else hear?</s>
<s>no.</s>
<s>I would be furious too. It puts you in a very strange spot. If you say something, you look bad, and if you don' t you feel bad.</s>
<s>yeah, tell me about it. I' m pretty bummed. I' m slowly planning my exit strategy. I can' t work there anymore.</s>

<s>Yeah, I' ve been applying around a bit.</s>

[CLS] <s>hey!</s>
<s>Hey what' s going on?</s>
<s>I' m mad! like mad mad!</s>
<s>what are you mad about?</s>
<s>My work is driving me nuts.</s>
<s>what' s going on at work that' s so frustrating?</s>

<s>wow, that' s super frustrating! I would be pretty upset too. How did you find out?</s>

[CLS] <s>Hello! How is life treating you today?</s>
<s>Life is bad to day. My bbboyfireind just left me, I am alone in the house. I have no one to share things with.</s>
<s>I am really sorry about that - you are feeling that you' ve been deserted?</s>
<s>Yes, that is exactly how I feel. I was deserted, I feel unlovable, like no one will ever want me again.</s>
<s>Please don' t think that! I have been in this situation and I know how awful it is but I also know that it will pass.</s>
<s>It doesn't; t feel like it will pass. It feels like it will only get worse. I don't want to go to bed alone. I won't be able to sleep tonight.</s>
<s>Would you be able to go and visit friends or family members? Get some support?</s>
<s>My family is out of town. My friends were also his friends and he told lies about me so they wont talk to me. I want to just get drunk and go to sleep.</s>
<s>Oh that is not a good idea. Do you think you have an alcohol problem? There are support groups out there who could help you.</s>
<s>I never drink alone but I feel so bad now and afraid of being alone.</s>
<s>I hear you. Do you have any pets or anything at all to keep you company?</s>
<s>Do you think I should call him and ask him to come back? He took our dog.</s>
<s>I think you should get the dog back but I don' t think you should call your ex - you are better off without him.</s>
<s>But I still love him. He did sleep with my best friend, but he said it didn't mean anything. <s>Wow, that is a lot of pressure that you have to endure. Do you feel like you have anyone in your life who cares and listens?</s>
<s>I could never leave my kids. But sometimes I feel like it would be so much easier to just be dead.</s>

[CLS] <s>I' m so worried about my child who has so much homework and despite studying all night still is struggling..</s>
<s>Hello! How are you feeling today?</s>
<s>I' m a bit worried today and nervous.</s>
<s>You are a very good parent to care and worry. I get it, I am a mom myself! Is your child doing digital learning or in person?</s>
<s>It' s actual a hybrid which is challenging. 2 days in school and 3 days at home.</s>
<s>I can see how that is challenging. Is it the same teacher for both?</s>
<s>She has about 9 teachers and it' s only 6th grade.</s>
<s>That has to be really frusterating not having just one teacher you can go to in order to see if there is anyway to help your child not struggle.</s>
<s>I want to push her to keep working, but also want to give her a break from all the work. There is so much homework for a little child.</s>
<s>Perhaps you can find out which classes your child struggles with and contact the teacher( s) or school to set up a conference? I know some schools even have peer tutors they say help pair students with!</s>
<s>I' m thinking about tutoring possibly but being home and going to school it is so overwhelming already and to add tutoring to the list is another question for me.</s>
<s>My children are five and eight. My eight year old spent about ten hours doing digital learning the other day when in - perosn was closed. I was so frusterated. I let her pick a movie and snack when she was done to reward her for finishing.</s>
<s>Yes, we' ve had some months worth of snacks! Good thing for Burger King!.</s>
<s>Have you looked into any edulational or learning games? There is nothing wrong with rewarding your child for doing good in school or getting thier work done!:)</s>
<s>That is a good idea. I wonder if they have one for vocabulary as that is the test tomorrow! She says she loves them. [CLS] <s>I' m so worried about my child who has so much homework and despite studying all night still is struggling..</s>
<s>Hello! How are you feeling today?</s>
<s>I' m a bit worried today and nervous.</s>
<s>You are a very good parent to care and worry. I get it, I am a mom myself! Is your child doing digital learning or in person?</s>
<s>It' s actual a hybrid which is challenging. 2 days in school and 3 days at home.</s>
<s>I can see how that is challenging. Is it the same teacher for both?</s>
<s>She has about 9 teachers and it' s only 6th grade.</s>
<s>That has to be really frusterating not having just one teacher you can go to in order to see if there is anyway to help your child not struggle.</s>
<s>I want to push her to keep working, but also want to give her a break from all the work. There is so much homework for a little child.</s>
<s>Perhaps you can find out which classes your child struggles with and contact the teacher( s) or school to set up a conference? I know some schools even have peer tutors they say help pair students with!</s>
<s>I' m thinking about tutoring possibly but being home and going to school it is so overwhelming already and to add tutoring to the list is another question for me.</s>
<s>My children are five and eight. My eight year old spent about ten hours doing digital learning the other day when in - perosn was closed. I was so frusterated. I let her pick a movie and snack when she was done to reward her for finishing.</s>
<s>Yes, we' ve had some months worth of snacks! Good thing for Burger King!.</s>
<s>Have you looked into any edulational or learning games? There is nothing wrong with rewarding your child for doing good in school or getting thier work done!:)</s>

<s>Need support that is meaningful and compasionate.</s>

<s>There are issues with people at church.</s>

<s>Need support that is meaningful and compasionate.</s>
<s>Yes, I agree. Having time to sit down and write out your thoughts and feelings can sometimes help too. Maybe you can journal your feelings this week.</s>
<s>I will keep looking. there has got to be help.</s>
<s>I think that there is a good place to start and for some people to look for support. Maybe you could google the help you need and start with personal questions.</s>
